title: Write a paragraph
prompts: Write a paragraph on the given topic.

title: Add content
prompts: Add 2-3 more sentences to the given content without changing anything else.

title: Generate ideas
prompts: Generate 3-5 ideas in bullet points based on the given topic.

title: Write a blog post

title: Generate a TL;DR
prompts: Summarize the given content in 1-2 sentences.

title: Write a summary
prompts: Write a summary of the given content in 1-2 paragraphs.

title: Paraphrase
prompts: Paraphrase the given content without changing the meaning.

title: Generate a tagline
prompts: Generate a catchy tagline for the given content.

title: Explain to a 2-year-old
prompts: Explain the given content in simple language suitable for a 2-year-old child.

title: Write a quote
prompts: Generate a relevant quote based on the given content.

title: Correct grammar
prompts: Correct any grammatical errors in the given content.

title: Generate a topic outline for blog
prompts: Create a topic outline for a blog post on the given topic.

title: Change tone
prompts: Change the tone of the given content to be more formal.

title: Make it conversational
prompts: Rewrite the given content to make it more conversational and friendly.

title: Adjust voice
prompts: Adjust the voice of the given content to be more authoritative and confident.

title: Proofread
prompts: Proofread the given content and correct any spelling or grammatical errors.

title: Fix spelling errors
prompts: Fix all spelling errors in the given content without making any other changes.

title: Add two lines

title: Add one line

title: Add a heading and a paragraph

title: Generate a Call-to-Action

title: Add Bullet Points
prompts: Add a list of bullet points to summarize this content

title: Expand on an Idea
prompts: Take one of the ideas in this content and expand on it

title: Improve Readability
prompts: Rewrite this content to improve its readability and flow

title: Add Examples
prompts: Add some examples to illustrate the points made in this content
